x = 0

while True:
    print("I am sleeping")
    x = input ("Did you set the alarm?")
    if x == "Yes":
        print("Wake up!!")
        break
    else:
        print("...")
        
        
    
    
   Explained: While true prints i am asleep forever, but asks did you set the alarm. if you answer yes it will break
   else it will also print ...
